dataList.content: Starbuck...! You... you were the only crew of the ship that could challenge Ahab.

dataList.title: Effloresced E.G.O::GasHarpoon
dataList.content: Starbuck was the first to kneel. It matters not how many waves a first mate has weathered... A first mate's station is still beneath his Captain...!

dataList.title: Effloresced E.G.O::GasHarpoon
dataList.content: Out of his own volition, He blinded his eyes in that complacent belief that regardless of whatever paths we took, the Captain would lead him to his destination!

dataList.title: Effloresced E.G.O::GasHarpoon
dataList.content: If you knew that he had sought a better path, then why have you not helped him see it?!

dataList.title: Effloresced E.G.O::GasHarpoon
dataList.content: So the fault lies with you again, Ishmael!
